                <br />
                <i>kache eshe joriye dhora baki</i>
                <br />
                <i>"bhalobashi tomake" bola baki</i>
                <br />
                <br />
                that yearning to just run back, not let go, to look at each other
                a few more minutes, to hug and never let go, and to announce to you
                and to the world that im deeply in love with you.
                <br />
                <br />
                <i>e jibon tomar name lekha baki</i>
                <br />
                <br />
                such sweet words in such a sweet languange. melts my heart. that
                leap of faith, that devotion, that surrendering of one's entire life
                at the mercy of another, compressed into five words.
