                your presence elevates everything, the time spent with you on my
                side is filled with joy and laughter, it's like attaching a window
                to the suffocating, windowless, damp and depressing room called my
                heart, you let in some fresh air.
                <br />
                <br />
                <i>bishonnota kete jay, tomar chhoay</i>
                <br />
                <i>je chhoa amar aro chaoa baki</i>
